hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ede2131f48c7eb2bd8e574cd39eb34c4bffe8683","tid":1553973,"uid":133728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T03:06:54.000Z","msg":"【民間記者會：908民意調查】<br />\n.<br />\n林鄭以四大行動回應五大訴求，你收唔收貨？香港市民有幾唔滿意政府黑警？快啲叫埋身邊同道中人一齊表達訴求，民間記者會同大家一齊發聲！民調去到星期一早上11時59分。link: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/908survey\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F908survey&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=9b5803e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/908survey</a> <br />\n.<br />\nDoes Carrie Lam's response to the 5 Demands with her 4 Major Actions cut it for you? How unhappy are fellow Hongkongers with the local authorities and the Hong Kong Police Force? Get your friends along and make your voices heard by filling in the survey below and we (the Citizens' Press Conference) will broadcast your views. Deadline for submission is 11:59am on Monday 9th September. Survey URL(please circulate widely): <a href=\"http://bit.ly/908survey\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F908survey&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=9b5803e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/908survey</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47cc34aef6887e3e0e15fa40f7485bc6b805716e","tid":1553973,"uid":184801,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T03:08:09.000Z","msg":"不如講明係&quot;答應&quot;而唔係&quot;回應&quot;五大訴求"},{"pid":"dadc061cc5f92dc5593cdf28c399c7c3997f0bbf","tid":1553973,"uid":133728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47cc34aef6887e3e0e15fa40f7485bc6b805716e","tid":1553973,"uid":184801,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T03:08:09.000Z","msg":"不如講明係&quot;答應&quot;而唔係&quot;回應&quot;五大訴求